                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-12-07</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>In short, this book does an excellent job at showing you how to perform statistical operations. However, it needs much improvement in explaining what the statistical operations are used for, and what their results tell a reader.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">It wasn't what I thought it would be</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
