                    <span>I purchased this book to help me in the second part of a two part course. The info in the book looks great, but unfortunately the info in the book stopped where I started at the begining of this semester. If you are looking for something to help with more in depth statitics,such as ANOVA analysis, then this book would not be of much help.</span>
                  
              
